Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <submodules> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT submodules (submodule*)>
 <!ATTLIST submodules
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
